title: Starbound.Beta.v.Frustrated.Koala-neO [PC/LINUX/MAC]
description:
Release Date: 13/12/10
Version: Frustrated Koala

This release Contains the FULL game for PC/LINUX/MAC
Doesn't require previous installation, but can be installed to update from "Annoyed Koala"

-Cracked!

Install:
Run the installer as admin
Select previous installation of starbound (if you just want to update)
Install, then play.
Run all game executables as administrator!

Troubleshoot:
If not starting try:
  -Closing Steam.
  -Installing DirectX.
  -Reinstalling game.


Multiplayer works over lan, and if ports are forwarded over internet.


Don't forget to keep seeding!
